Title: Entropy for extremal Reissner- Nordstr\o m black holes
Authors: Amit Ghosh and P. Mitra
Comments: 7 pages, latex
Report-no: SISSA-172/94/EP
Journal-ref: Phys. Lett. B357 (1995) 295
\\
  We reinterpret recent work on extremal Reissner- Nordstr\o m black holes to
argue that the mass is a measure of the gravitational entropy. We also find
that the entropy of scalar fields in this background has a stronger divergence
than usual.
